name: Seattle Sports RS - SUP Carrier Kit
description: Transport your paddleboard or sit-on-top kayak.Non-skid laminate won't slip even on a wet surface.Compatible with factory racks, after market roof racks, or can be used without a rack.Stacker blocks allow you to transport 2 boards.Includes 2 universal foam blocks, 2 SUP stacker blocks, 2 block straps (9ft.), 2 center straps with cam buckle (15ft.).SUP/SOT universal block dimensions are 3.75x 4.75 x 31.5in.SUP stacker block dimensions are 1.25 x 4.75 x 23.25in.
